#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2020-07-10-quarkus-test-profiles.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Quarkus now supports test profiles"
msgstr "Quarkus现在支持测试配置文件"

#: _posts/2020-07-10-quarkus-test-profiles.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"With the release of Quarkus 1.6 Quarkus now supports test profiles, allowing "
"you to easily test multiple different configurations\n"
"inside the same module. This post outlines what test profiles are and how "
"you can use them."
msgstr ""
"随着 Quarkus 1.6 的发布，Quarkus "
"现在支持测试配置文件，让你可以轻松地测试同一模块内的多个不同配置。本文章概述了什么是测试配置文件以及如何使用它们。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2020-07-10-quarkus-test-profiles.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Recap on how `@QuarkusTest` works"
msgstr "回顾一下 `@QuarkusTest` 的工作方式"

#: _posts/2020-07-10-quarkus-test-profiles.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Before we talk about test profiles let's talk briefly about how "
"`@QuarkusTest` annotated tests actually work. The first time\n"
"one of these tests is run the Quarkus test extension will start Quarkus. "
"Quarkus will then remain running for the duration\n"
"of the test run. This makes testing very fast, because Quarkus is only "
"started once, however it does limit you to testing\n"
"a single configuration per module, as you can't restart Quarkus in a "
"different configuration. Test profiles lift this\n"
"limitation."
msgstr ""
"在讨论测试配置文件之前，我们先简单谈谈 `@QuarkusTest` 注释测试的实际工作原理。第一次运行这些测试时，Quarkus 测试扩展会启动 "
"Quarkus。然后，Quarkus 将在测试运行期间保持运行。由于 Quarkus "
"只启动一次，因此测试速度非常快，但这也限制了你只能测试每个模块的单一配置，因为你无法在不同配置下重新启动 Quarkus。测试配置文件取消了这一限制。"

