#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2020-07-10-quarkus-test-profiles.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "How it works"
msgstr "它是如何工作的"

#: _posts/2020-07-10-quarkus-test-profiles.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Before a `@QuarkusTest` is executed the Quarkus test extension will check "
"the profile that the test wants to use, and compares\n"
"it to the profile that was used by the last test. If they are the same then "
"no action is taken, the currently running\n"
"Quarkus application is already using the correct profile. If they are "
"different then Quarkus is stopped, and then started\n"
"with the new config."
msgstr ""
"在执行 `@QuarkusTest` 之前，Quarkus "
"测试扩展将检查测试要使用的配置文件，并将其与上次测试使用的配置文件进行比较。如果两者相同，则不采取任何措施，因为当前运行的 Quarkus "
"应用程序已经使用了正确的配置文件。如果两者不同，则停止 Quarkus，然后使用新配置启动。"

#: _posts/2020-07-10-quarkus-test-profiles.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In general it is best to stop and start Quarkus as few times as possible for "
"the fastest possible test runs. To do\n"
"this it is recommended that you run your tests in alphabetical order, and "
"configure all tests that require specific profiles\n"
"into their own package. This means that all tests with the same profile will "
"be run together, so Quarkus will be restarted\n"
"a minimal number of times."
msgstr ""
"一般来说，为了以最快的速度运行测试，最好尽可能少地停止和启动 "
"Quarkus。为此，建议按字母顺序运行测试，并将所有需要特定配置文件的测试配置到自己的软件包中。这意味着具有相同配置文件的所有测试都将一起运行，因此重新启动 "
"Quarkus 的次数将减少到最低限度。"

